title: MNA Ihsanullah Tiwana meets prime minister
content:
ISLAMABAD, Oct 14 (APP): Member of the National Assembly Ihsanullah Tiwana Thursday called on Prime Minister Imran Khan here.
During the meeting, they discussed the matters pertaining to the parliamentarianâ€™s constituency and ongoing development projects there.
Special Assistant to PM on Political Affairs Malik Amir Dogar was also present.
